	 it's like to own a part of Washington's first co-op brewery. Whether you’
	re a die-hard hop head or just co-op curious\, this is your opportunity to
	 sip\, socialize\, and see what membership is all about — no commitment re
	quired.Expect fresh pours\, good vibes\, and even better beerSaturday 5/10
	 and Tuesday 5/13Come thirsty\, leave inspired — and maybe even as our new
	est co-op member. Cheers to community\, craft\, and cold ones!\n\nFrom Sea
	ttle Beer Week
